The paper deals with a problem in natural language processing, specifically in machine reading comprehension. The paper proposes a novel neural network system that optimizes keyword-based queries and finds answers from a given passage. This falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
